txt.en: Defeat many beasts and insects in the Vales of Anduin.

'While I was away, many beasts and insects succumbed to the spreading darkness. I am so sorry, my friends! I am here now to set things aright, if I can! I will do my best, yes, I will do my very best!' - Radagast the Brown
